          Building on this foundation, the platform provides cryptographic verification for every credential issued. Recipients receive badges with blockchain timestamps that serve as permanent proof of authenticity. As a result, employers and institutions can verify credentials instantly through public verification links without contacting the issuing organization. <a href="https://docs.bws.ninja/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Blockchain Badges documentation</a> explains the technical verification process in detail.
        </p>
        <h3><strong>Visual Designer and Bulk Issuance</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Beyond verification capabilities, the platform includes a visual badge designer that enables institutions to create professional credential templates. Organizations can then issue certificates individually or in bulk for graduating classes and training programs.
        </p>
        <p>
