        </p>
        <h3><strong>Recipient Control and Sharing</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Once credentials are issued, recipients gain full control over their verified badges and can share them across professional networks. Each badge includes a verification link that employers can use to confirm authenticity instantly—no waiting, no phone calls.
        </p>
        <p>
